<sec>
<st>
West Virginia</st>

<p>

After his one season at <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../903/303903.xml">
UTEP</link>, Casteel traveled to <university wordnetid="108286163" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../979/185979.xml">
West Virginia University</link></university>
 to head coach <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
<person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.8">
<player wordnetid="110439851" confidence="0.8">
<contestant wordnetid="109613191" confidence="0.8">
